Solr
====

This plugin is still in heavy development: do not use in production!


Development setup
-----------------

    $ cd /opt
    $ wget http://mirror.ibcp.fr/pub/apache//lucene/solr/3.5.0/apache-solr-3.5.0.tgz
    $ tar zxf apache-solr-3.5.0.tgz
    $ cd apache-solr-3.5.0/example/
    $ java -jar start.jar


